mod-millercolumns-padding.description:
Used by `.spectrum-MillerColumns`.
Defaults to `var(--spectrum-spacing-100)`, if not set.

mod-millercolumns-margin-inline-end.description:
Used by `.spectrum-MillerColumns-item`.
Defaults to `var(--spectrum-spacing-100)`, if not set.

mod-millercolumns-margin-inline-start.description:
Used by `.spectrum-MillerColumns-item:first-child`.
Defaults to `var(--spectrum-spacing-100)`, if not set.
